---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-black border-t border-slate-900 py-16 px-6 mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white tracking-widest uppercase">
          TRADE<span class="text-emerald-500">90</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">
          Position size calculator and risk discipline system built for US funded traders.
          The Trade90 Safety System: 0.5% max per trade, 1% daily cap — designed to protect your
          prop firm challenge from oversizing and cascade drawdowns.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
          <span class="text-emerald-400 text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest">Safety System Active</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Funded Traders</h4>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/funded-trader-risk-calculator/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:text-white text-xs uppercase font-black transition-colors">Funded Risk Calculator</a>
          <a href="/ftmo-position-size-calculator/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">FTMO Calculator</a>
          <a href="/prop-firm-risk-management/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">Prop Firm Risk Guide</a>
          <a href="/how-to-calculate-position-size/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">How to Size Positions</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">Market Analysis</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">About</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Calculators</h4>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/calculator/eurusd/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-green-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">EUR/USD Calculator</a>
          <a href="/calculator/xauusd/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-green-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">Gold (XAU/USD) Calculator</a>
          <a href="/calculator/gbpusd/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-green-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">GBP/USD Calculator</a>
          <a href="/calculator/nas100/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-green-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">NAS100 Calculator</a>
          <a href="/pip-value-calculator/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-green-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">Pip Value Calculator</a>
          <a href="/risk-reward-calculator/" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-green-500 text-xs uppercase font-bold transition-colors">Risk Reward Calculator</a>
          <a href="/calculator/" class="text-green-500 hover:text-white text-xs uppercase font-black transition-colors">All 45+ Instruments →</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-slate-300 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Risk Disclosure</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-tight italic">
          Trading involves significant risk of loss and is not suitable for all investors.
          The Trade90 Safety System (0.5% per trade / 1% daily) is TRADE90's internal risk
          discipline framework — not an official prop firm rule. Always verify your firm's
          specific drawdown rules. TRADE90 provides tools and education, not financial advice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-900/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6">
        <a href="/disclaimer" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold transition-colors underline decoration-slate-800 underline-offset-4">Legal Disclaimer</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold transition-colors underline decoration-slate-800 underline-offset-4">Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-mono">
        &copy; {currentYear} TRADE90 — RISK DISCIPLINE FOR US FUNDED TRADERS
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
